{"tid":1744913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[教化]大家行駛左你屋企既絡網權未 youtube & router","createTime":"2019-11-22T03:31:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T09:41:16.000Z","uid":57633,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d1d241222fa38555a49beb041a1361556ec352b2","tid":1744913,"uid":57633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:31:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">tldr可以睇紅字</span><br />\n<br />\n事緣我有個煮食 youtube channel想比屋企人睇<br />\n等佢改進下d廚藝<br />\n<br />\n點知一入到去佢youtube就見到成版都係大量垃圾深藍片<br />\n即時忍唔住大叫屌你老 _ <br />\n<br />\n咁嬲完都要諗點解決既<br />\n但youtube好鬼低能<br />\n有得follow 鍾意既channel<br />\n但就無得入d特定channel去block濕佢<br />\n<br />\n雖然都唔係完全無得block<br />\n不過就要辛苦d<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">係youtube首頁見一條片block 一個channel<br />\n圖如下, 指住條片名, 等出3粒點, 再按尾2&rdquo; 不要推薦這個頻道&rdquo;</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ooQ7NPJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FooQ7NPJ.jpg&h=4a8760d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBlock到咁上下都未完<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你要幫佢follow返d 黃色channel</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黃色channel List 有人想知再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於呢個工程十分之漫長<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以都建議大家用電腦登入佢地youtube email<br />\n再係電腦慢慢執<br />\n<br />\n大家有咩問題或者有咩黃色channel share<br />\n都可以大家係到討論下<br />\n我遲d再整返個list, 方便大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />另外, 如果你識整個router , 記得block 9 tvb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n封鎖字眼就得<br />\n例如 tvb, mytvsuper"},{"pid":"cc0a46a2944f1e6e169787ce2bc447407ce43ff6","tid":1744913,"uid":281516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:32:24.000Z","msg":"選舉近了, 共黨B隊出動!!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1744825\" data-auto-